            <p class="invite_text1">What is www.keupons?</p>
            <p>
             <%=auto_link( "www.keupons.com is the new way in social and group buying. Almost continuously it keeps updating new deals on the site. Each day, keupons.com features unbeatable deals on the best stuff to do, see, eat, and buy in your city. By promising businesses a customers, we get discounts you won't find anywhere else. </p><p>
Increasing Discounts: At Keupons.com we believe that EVERYONE should get the best possible discount! And living with our aim of More the merrier”, our deals are made in such a way that as MORE people sign-up for a deal the discount INCREASES! 
You will see that whenever you click at a deal there is a ‘slider’  showing that number of people who have ‘bought’ and the current discount. And as the number of people who buy the deal increases so does the discount. </p><p>
